long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
You can open Google services with one click. Every time a new tab is opened, you will see Google services.

Install
By clicking "Add to Chrome", I accept and agree to install 'Gtab New Tab for Google Services Gsuite' Сhrome extension and set the chrome new tab to that provided by the service and the terms of use and privacy policy.
